[LOG](../../../logs/2011/2011-06-08-log.txt).


## President's Report

Bdale thanked Joshua Drake and his company Command Prompt for their continuing
support of SPI. The SPI admin team recently moved a webapp used by our
treasurer from a physical server installed on 28 October 2006 to a virtual
machine. It is only through the ongoing generosity of Command Prompt and our
other resource donors that SPI is able to provide services to our associated
projects.


